      • collectMinMaxInformation

        public static void collectMinMaxInformation(gov.nasa.jpf.Config config)
        Collects information about the lower and upper bounds on integer and real symbolic variables, and specific bounds for variables, given by name. The default bounds are now specified as follows: 
         symbolic.min_int = 0
 symbolic.max_int = 999
 symbolic.min_double = -0.5
 symbolic.max_double = 1.5
        To specific a overriding bound for symbolic variables "abc " and "xyz", we write 
         symbolic.min_int_abc = 10
 symbolic.max_int_abc = 99
 symbolic.min_double_xyz = -0.9
 symbolic.max_double_xyz = 0.9
        Parameters:
        config - the JPF configuration file
